306
00:17:44,395 --> 00:17:47,095
Therefore, Mika was ecstatic.

307
00:17:47,095 --> 00:17:50,995
I've been waiting all this time for this moment to come!

308
00:17:50,995 --> 00:17:54,895
Thank you so much, Koji.

309
00:17:54,895 --> 00:17:58,995
